<h2 style="color=firebrick">Welcome to the world of </h2>
<span style="font-size:50;color=#CC3300"><b>Indian  Art  Music</b></span>
<br>
<span style="font-size:22;color=#CC3300"><b>(Raga Music, Hindustani Music, Indian Classical Music)</b></span>
<br><br>
<span style="font-size:18;color=maroon"><b>Here you will learn about the features of this glorious and sophisticated form of music. 
<br>
You will also meet here with two of its most authentic and senior practitioners, who are at once concert performers, scholars, composers and teachers.
<br><br>
Furthermore, this website will introduce you to diverse facets of Indian classical culture.
<br>
This is a living site, with additional material being constantly added, so be sure to visit frequently!

</b>
</span>

